    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>欢迎来到地下竞技场 —— 混乱与竞争的终极战场！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将肩负使命，在充满矿物、强化道具与敌对鼹鼠的可破坏洞穴中一路挖掘、突进。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采集资源、智斗对手，在这款专为 2 至 8 名玩家打造的快节奏派对对战游戏中，将矿物成功运送交付，赢得最终胜利！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战斗、爆破、冲刺 —— 混战一触即发！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 利用喷气背包加速运输矿物，但要小心，其他鼹鼠会用尽一切手段来抢走你的成果！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>挖掘与破坏</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穿越动态生成的地图，每 局都不尽相同。边挖掘、边战斗和破坏，改变战场地形，争取最终胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204560/extras/55fecffbb8d873b9fd869a12c3eb7191.poster.avif?t=1766565219\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204560/extras/55fecffbb8d873b9fd869a12c3eb7191.webm?t=1766565219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204560/extras/55fecffbb8d873b9fd869a12c3eb7191.mp4?t=1766565219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>按你的方式游玩</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 混搭独特的工具和装置。掌握你最爱的组合，对抗好友的策略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204560/extras/24d5191065510de8b991bf657bfd3ac6.poster.avif?t=1766565219\" width=852 height=466 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204560/extras/24d5191065510de8b991bf657bfd3ac6.webm?t=1766565219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204560/extras/24d5191065510de8b991bf657bfd3ac6.mp4?t=1766565219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>混乱的 PvP 地下大乱斗</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持最多 8 人混战或组队对抗！在这片不可预测的地下竞技场中，比速度、拼策略、看谁挖得又快又狠。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204560/extras/0e5d2e74683503e88590c4cd1db03112.poster.avif?t=1766565219\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204560/extras/0e5d2e74683503e88590c4cd1db03112.webm?t=1766565219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204560/extras/0e5d2e74683503e88590c4cd1db03112.mp4?t=1766565219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>为派对而生的欢乐战局</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拿起手柄，叫上好友、对战 AI，或在线匹配陌生玩家，随时加入一场酣畅淋漓的快速对局！《深岩狂鼠》全面支持手柄操作，轻松上手，欢乐不断！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204560/extras/86fc5a48523b8593ab8737734127bdcc.poster.avif?t=1766565219\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204560/extras/86fc5a48523b8593ab8737734127bdcc.webm?t=1766565219\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2204560/extras/86fc5a48523b8593ab8737734127bdcc.mp4?t=1766565219\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
